1
00:00:24,280 --> 00:00:24,920
Brother.

2
00:00:31,440 --> 00:00:32,350
What are these?

3
00:00:34,830 --> 00:00:40,500
[Chief of Great Yan's Helian Tribe,
Helian Chuan]

4
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:37,520
I have some good news for you.

5
00:00:37,520 --> 00:00:39,380
Elder Tubo of the Hongchuan Tribe

6
00:00:39,430 --> 00:00:41,200
wants to take you as his concubine.

7
00:00:41,200 --> 00:00:42,000
Look at these.

8
00:00:42,280 --> 00:00:44,000
These are all
the betrothal gifts they sent—

9
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:46,160
a full twenty-something chests of them.

10
00:00:46,160 --> 00:00:46,920
Look.

11
00:00:48,240 --> 00:00:48,970
Look at these

12
00:00:49,070 --> 00:00:50,470
gold and silver jewelry.

13
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:55,360
Elder Tubo also promised

14
00:00:55,920 --> 00:00:57,450
that after you get married,

15
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:59,430
he will give us 500 horses

16
00:00:59,430 --> 00:01:01,000
and 200 acres of pasture.

17
00:01:01,430 --> 00:01:02,490
Two hundred acres.

18
00:01:03,430 --> 00:01:04,590
Our Helian Tribe hasn't been

19
00:01:04,590 --> 00:01:06,190
this glorious in a long time.

20
00:01:09,039 --> 00:01:10,770
Elder Tubo is over 70 years old.

21
00:01:11,590 --> 00:01:13,310
He also already has
three wives and concubines.

22
00:01:13,310 --> 00:01:14,000
Brother,

23
00:01:14,310 --> 00:01:15,840
you're not joking, are you?

24
00:01:16,430 --> 00:01:17,760
My dear sister,

25
00:01:18,590 --> 00:01:20,280
you should be sensible.

26
00:01:21,480 --> 00:01:22,150
Yes,

27
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:25,430
Elder Tubo is a bit old.

28
00:01:26,510 --> 00:01:27,510
But you also know

29
00:01:27,950 --> 00:01:29,080
the Hongchuan Tribe

30
00:01:29,130 --> 00:01:30,710
is the most powerful

31
00:01:30,710 --> 00:01:32,310
of the 13 tribes in Great Yan.

32
00:01:32,660 --> 00:01:34,180
He is a bit old,

33
00:01:34,509 --> 00:01:36,840
but his wives and concubines
are not young either.

34
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:38,470
Even if you marry him as a concubine now

35
00:01:38,470 --> 00:01:41,140
and bear him a child,

36
00:01:41,229 --> 00:01:42,070
in a few years,

37
00:01:42,070 --> 00:01:44,600
when he
and his wives and concubines are gone,

38
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:47,039
this Hongchuan Tribe

39
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:49,810
will become the backyard
of our Helian Tribe.

40
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:56,440
Just thinking about it makes me happy.

41
00:01:57,180 --> 00:01:58,630
Give up on that idea.

42
00:01:59,310 --> 00:02:00,640
Mind your own business.

43
00:02:06,770 --> 00:02:08,289
Yan Xun will not marry you.

44
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:09,940
For that female slave,

45
00:02:10,310 --> 00:02:12,840
he even stopped fighting
the war with Great Yong.

46
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,500
You still expect to marry him?

47
00:02:14,630 --> 00:02:15,910
Stop daydreaming!

48
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:18,240
Do you think

49
00:02:18,630 --> 00:02:20,190
the Hongchuan Tribe
giving you a few horses

50
00:02:20,190 --> 00:02:21,150
can bring back the past glory

51
00:02:21,150 --> 00:02:22,360
our Helian Tribe had?

52
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:23,390
Let me tell you,

53
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,400
even if you sell me to Tubo,

54
00:02:25,710 --> 00:02:28,030
the tribes of Great Yan
will still look down on you.

55
00:02:28,030 --> 00:02:29,630
You will still be the worthless prodigal

56
00:02:29,630 --> 00:02:30,650
mocked by those tribe elders,

57
00:02:30,650 --> 00:02:31,120
the—

58
00:02:33,190 --> 00:02:34,520
I'm warning you:

59
00:02:35,180 --> 00:02:37,650
Obediently marry Elder Tubo.

60
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:40,310
Otherwise, I'll strangle you to death

61
00:02:40,310 --> 00:02:42,800
and send your corpse to him.

62
00:04:17,470 --> 00:04:22,600
[REBIRTH]

63
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:25,530
[Episode 11]

64
00:05:15,770 --> 00:05:16,690
General Cheng,

65
00:05:17,270 --> 00:05:18,870
what else do you want from me?

66
00:05:19,190 --> 00:05:21,830
Do you, Lady Helian,
feel that I, Cheng Yuan, have lost power

67
00:05:21,830 --> 00:05:23,480
so you don't even want to see me?

68
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:25,240
General Cheng, why say that?

69
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:26,720
I am just

70
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:28,920
an ordinary female officer in the army.

71
00:05:29,310 --> 00:05:31,270
What makes me capable
of being a fair-weather friend

72
00:05:31,270 --> 00:05:32,870
and looking down on you, General Cheng?

73
00:05:32,870 --> 00:05:35,159
It's just that
I can hardly protect myself now.

74
00:05:35,159 --> 00:05:36,680
I'm afraid it's not like before,

75
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:38,680
and I can't help you with anything.

76
00:05:38,870 --> 00:05:39,680
What if I said

77
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,750
I am here to help you?

78
00:05:42,409 --> 00:05:43,610
Would you believe it?

79
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:48,600
I address you as General Cheng

80
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:51,560
only because of our past alliance.

81
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:53,630
You are a stray dog now,

82
00:05:53,870 --> 00:05:54,930
how can you help me?

83
00:05:57,090 --> 00:05:58,800
I am a stray dog, indeed,

84
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:01,930
but I am also the one
who knows Yan Xun best.

85
00:06:07,590 --> 00:06:09,050
What are you trying to say?

86
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:14,830
I can help you

87
00:06:15,870 --> 00:06:17,480
become Yan Xun's queen.

88
00:06:25,650 --> 00:06:26,980
What do you want me to do?

89
00:06:47,190 --> 00:06:47,950
Strange.

90
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:50,270
In the past,
when this black eagle saw His Majesty,

91
00:06:50,270 --> 00:06:51,159
it would stop.

92
00:06:51,510 --> 00:06:53,510
Why is it acting so abnormal today?

93
00:06:55,190 --> 00:06:56,000
It's Chu.

94
00:06:56,790 --> 00:06:58,650
The black eagle brought Chu back!

95
00:07:24,870 --> 00:07:25,560
Chu.

96
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,190
Your Majesty.

97
00:07:43,630 --> 00:07:45,690
Why did you call for this black eagle?

98
00:07:46,870 --> 00:07:47,720
Your Majesty,

99
00:07:48,510 --> 00:07:50,190
I have never seen this black eagle before,

100
00:07:50,190 --> 00:07:51,850
nor do I know how to call for it.

101
00:07:52,870 --> 00:07:54,480
It flew over

102
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,520
while I was practicing horse riding.

103
00:07:55,520 --> 00:07:56,659
Maybe it was tired of flying

104
00:07:56,659 --> 00:07:58,520
and wanted to stop and have a rest.

105
00:08:01,950 --> 00:08:02,680
Is this eagle

106
00:08:02,950 --> 00:08:04,600
raised by Your Majesty?

107
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:07,880
I see a white silk ribbon tied to its leg.

108
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:10,500
This is a custom of Great Yan's herdsmen
to make a wish.

109
00:08:10,500 --> 00:08:13,360
Does Your Majesty
have any wish you wish to fulfill?

110
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:19,240
Why do you suddenly
want to learn horse riding?

111
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:21,870
Because Your Majesty
has been either hunting in the paddock

112
00:08:21,870 --> 00:08:24,430
or leading people
to look around for Queen Chu.

113
00:08:24,430 --> 00:08:25,750
I want to help Your Majesty.

114
00:08:25,750 --> 00:08:27,510
Even if we can't find Queen Chu,

115
00:08:27,540 --> 00:08:29,630
I can accompany Your Majesty to hunt

116
00:08:29,750 --> 00:08:30,600
and relax.

117
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:36,080
I'll teach you how to ride a horse.

118
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:36,870
Come with me.

119
00:10:27,550 --> 00:10:28,440
Chu...

120
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:31,510
Chu?

121
00:10:33,270 --> 00:10:35,000
I asked Black Eagle to find you.

122
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:36,840
Did...

123
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:39,210
Did Black Eagle bring you back?

124
00:10:39,550 --> 00:10:40,200
Yes.

125
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,150
Yan Xun.

126
00:10:44,770 --> 00:10:45,680
Look at me.

127
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:47,720
I'm Chu.

128
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:49,870
Chu.

129
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:51,550
I miss you so much.

130
00:11:02,350 --> 00:11:03,110
Yan Xun.

131
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:05,630
I'm Chu.

132
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:07,810
I am your Chu.

133
00:11:14,710 --> 00:11:15,840
I missed you so much.

134
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:17,640
Your Majesty.

135
00:11:18,870 --> 00:11:19,870
Let's drink.

136
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:54,150
Chu,

137
00:11:55,180 --> 00:11:56,300
where did you go?

138
00:11:57,350 --> 00:11:58,780
I really missed you.

139
00:13:01,360 --> 00:13:03,490
Greetings, Princess Consort Helian.

140
00:13:05,740 --> 00:13:06,870
What did you call me?

141
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:09,690
His Majesty has announced to Great Yan

142
00:13:09,690 --> 00:13:11,690
that you are appointed
as the Secondary Princess Consort of Great Yan.

143
00:13:11,690 --> 00:13:14,220
Congratulations, Princess Consort Helian.

144
00:13:15,710 --> 00:13:17,960
[Tangjing, Biantang]

145
00:13:25,750 --> 00:13:27,390
Is Beauty Han here?

146
00:13:28,320 --> 00:13:29,080
Beauty Han,

147
00:13:29,870 --> 00:13:31,330
I have prepared for you...

148
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:35,160
Oh, it's the Empress.

149
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:38,550
Greetings, Your Majesty.

150
00:13:38,550 --> 00:13:41,080
I must ask for your forgiveness
for one thing.

151
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:42,610
I failed in raising our son,

152
00:13:42,870 --> 00:13:44,750
causing him to made a grave mistake.

153
00:13:44,750 --> 00:13:46,080
What has Ce done now?

154
00:13:54,270 --> 00:13:55,070
Your Majesty,

155
00:13:55,600 --> 00:13:57,530
Princess Fu, whom Ce brought back,

156
00:13:57,670 --> 00:13:59,510
is actually a criminal slave
from Great Yong,

157
00:13:59,510 --> 00:14:02,270
Chu Qiao,
a general of Great Yan's Xiuli Army.

158
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:04,320
I originally thought

159
00:14:04,320 --> 00:14:06,720
Ce was just acting absurdly

160
00:14:06,790 --> 00:14:08,870
which was why
he had feelings for that woman.

161
00:14:08,870 --> 00:14:12,240
So I turned a blind eye

162
00:14:12,480 --> 00:14:13,670
and let him be.

163
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:15,860
But at the state banquet that day,

164
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:17,130
he and Chu Qiao

165
00:14:17,160 --> 00:14:19,280
echoed each other with King of Ximeng,

166
00:14:19,280 --> 00:14:20,480
colluding secretly.

167
00:14:21,780 --> 00:14:22,690
I suspect

168
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:25,390
Ce might be secretly colluding

169
00:14:25,690 --> 00:14:26,810
with Ximeng.

170
00:14:30,150 --> 00:14:31,480
You mean

171
00:14:32,030 --> 00:14:35,120
Ce colluded
with General Chu Qiao of Great Yan

172
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:37,870
and the King of Ximeng,

173
00:14:38,120 --> 00:14:38,670
right?

174
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:43,060
Does Your Majesty find this amusing?

175
00:14:43,480 --> 00:14:44,630
I think

176
00:14:45,360 --> 00:14:49,080
since we Biantang
are bordering Great Yan and Great Yong,

177
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:52,440
now that they are at war,

178
00:14:53,150 --> 00:14:56,240
no matter who wins or loses in the end,

179
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:58,630
it wouldn't be a good thing for Biantang.

180
00:14:59,910 --> 00:15:02,320
If Ce can really make Ximeng

181
00:15:02,440 --> 00:15:04,510
an ally of Biantang,

182
00:15:04,600 --> 00:15:07,320
that would indeed relieve
one of my worries.

183
00:15:09,910 --> 00:15:12,030
Does Your Majesty really think so?

184
00:15:13,360 --> 00:15:15,080
As for this Chu Qiao,

185
00:15:15,790 --> 00:15:18,000
if Ce likes her, let him be.

186
00:15:18,920 --> 00:15:20,380
She's just a female slave.

187
00:15:20,960 --> 00:15:22,440
Besides, I've heard

188
00:15:22,870 --> 00:15:26,200
this slave once helped
Heir Apparent Yan rebel.

189
00:15:26,830 --> 00:15:28,070
I saw her that day too.

190
00:15:28,240 --> 00:15:29,370
She is quick-witted

191
00:15:29,550 --> 00:15:30,630
and capable.

192
00:15:30,880 --> 00:15:32,640
If she can be used by Ce,

193
00:15:33,270 --> 00:15:34,530
it's also a good thing.

194
00:15:34,550 --> 00:15:35,440
But this Chu Qiao's

195
00:15:35,440 --> 00:15:37,670
relationship with Heir Apparent Yan
is extremely complicated.

196
00:15:37,670 --> 00:15:39,670
I am not at ease letting her marry Ce.

197
00:15:43,750 --> 00:15:44,750
Isn't that

198
00:15:44,790 --> 00:15:47,500
exactly what you and I want?

199
00:15:47,890 --> 00:15:49,130
If we

200
00:15:49,320 --> 00:15:51,980
had not gone through
all those twists and turns,

201
00:15:52,270 --> 00:15:55,670
we wouldn't be in such harmony today.

202
00:15:59,150 --> 00:15:59,960
Someone,

203
00:16:00,280 --> 00:16:01,880
bring the snacks I prepared.

204
00:16:05,480 --> 00:16:08,110
This is your favourite pastry,

205
00:16:08,110 --> 00:16:09,630
Milk Poria Crisp Custard,

206
00:16:10,270 --> 00:16:12,670
I had the imperial kitchen
prepare for you.

207
00:16:13,150 --> 00:16:14,600
Come, have a taste.

208
00:16:27,570 --> 00:16:28,970
Thank you, Your Majesty,

209
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:32,600
for remembering
my preference after all these years.

210
00:16:43,840 --> 00:16:44,480
Leave.

211
00:16:45,040 --> 00:16:45,590
Yes.

212
00:16:50,390 --> 00:16:51,190
Your Majesty,

213
00:16:51,670 --> 00:16:53,600
don't ruin your health with anger.

214
00:16:53,790 --> 00:16:55,320
I will definitely do my best

215
00:16:56,150 --> 00:16:57,240
to plan for you.

216
00:17:16,880 --> 00:17:17,680
Your Majesty,

217
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:19,030
His Majesty not only sent people

218
00:17:19,030 --> 00:17:20,680
to deliver
those gold, silver and brocades,

219
00:17:20,680 --> 00:17:21,720
but also specifically ordered

220
00:17:21,720 --> 00:17:22,829
that your meals in the future

221
00:17:22,829 --> 00:17:24,160
will be made by the small kitchen.

222
00:17:24,160 --> 00:17:25,720
He said the chef in the small kitchen

223
00:17:25,720 --> 00:17:28,520
is best at making
the Poria Crisp Custard you love.

224
00:17:29,140 --> 00:17:29,970
Your Majesty!

225
00:17:32,160 --> 00:17:32,960
Your Majesty.

226
00:17:34,300 --> 00:17:35,630
What's wrong, Yan Qing?

227
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:40,680
Heir Apparent...

228
00:17:42,650 --> 00:17:44,450
What happened to Heir Apparent?

229
00:17:44,560 --> 00:17:47,020
News came
from the Prince of Chang's mansion

230
00:17:47,640 --> 00:17:49,790
that Heir Apparent caught a plague...

231
00:17:51,310 --> 00:17:52,310
and passed away.

232
00:17:58,940 --> 00:17:59,530
What?

233
00:18:00,290 --> 00:18:01,900
Heir Apparent...

234
00:18:03,830 --> 00:18:05,240
passed away.

235
00:18:07,160 --> 00:18:07,960
Your Majesty!

236
00:18:08,440 --> 00:18:09,030
Your Majesty!

237
00:18:09,030 --> 00:18:09,790
Impossible.

238
00:18:10,100 --> 00:18:11,110
Xu is not dead.

239
00:18:11,110 --> 00:18:12,000
I'm going to find him.

240
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:12,590
Your Majesty.

241
00:18:12,590 --> 00:18:13,350
I'm going to find him.

242
00:18:13,350 --> 00:18:14,160
Your Majesty.

243
00:18:14,160 --> 00:18:15,030
Let me go!

244
00:18:17,120 --> 00:18:17,920
Your Majesty.

245
00:18:27,790 --> 00:18:29,510
Xu!

246
00:18:30,270 --> 00:18:32,310
Your Majesty.

247
00:18:33,160 --> 00:18:34,200
Your Majesty!

248
00:18:34,310 --> 00:18:35,240
Your Majesty!

249
00:18:35,640 --> 00:18:36,400
Your Majesty.

250
00:18:36,400 --> 00:18:38,550
Xu!

251
00:18:50,070 --> 00:18:50,920
He who couldn't tolerate

252
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:52,850
my son with Crown Prince Maocheng,

253
00:18:54,220 --> 00:18:55,420
so he killed Xu.

254
00:18:58,330 --> 00:18:59,610
He lied to me.

255
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:03,510
He said he would spare Xu.

256
00:19:05,390 --> 00:19:07,390
Yet he used such a despicable method

257
00:19:08,510 --> 00:19:09,790
to kill him.

258
00:19:10,810 --> 00:19:11,890
It's my fault.

259
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:14,160
I was incompetent.

260
00:19:15,350 --> 00:19:17,480
I failed to eliminate Chu Qiao for you,

261
00:19:18,200 --> 00:19:20,400
causing you to suffer such a grievance.

262
00:19:21,440 --> 00:19:23,370
Your Majesty, please don't be sad.

263
00:19:23,900 --> 00:19:25,380
Just punish me.

264
00:19:49,510 --> 00:19:50,240
Lord Zhan.

265
00:19:50,590 --> 00:19:52,590
Her Majesty sentenced you to 40 lashes.

266
00:19:52,590 --> 00:19:54,270
You should put your clothes on.

267
00:19:54,270 --> 00:19:55,070
Otherwise...

268
00:19:55,110 --> 00:19:56,980
Otherwise,
you'll be beaten to a bloody pulp.

269
00:19:56,980 --> 00:19:58,550
That is what I deserve.

270
00:19:59,260 --> 00:20:00,910
I must remember this pain,

271
00:20:01,550 --> 00:20:03,550
so I won't disappoint her.

272
00:20:04,550 --> 00:20:05,590
Continue!

273
00:20:24,070 --> 00:20:25,400
Last time in the palace,

274
00:20:25,400 --> 00:20:26,160
Her Majesty already noticed

275
00:20:26,160 --> 00:20:28,510
the connection between us
and King of Ximeng.

276
00:20:28,510 --> 00:20:29,480
Before she figures out

277
00:20:29,480 --> 00:20:30,550
our relationship

278
00:20:30,640 --> 00:20:31,880
and makes a move against us,

279
00:20:31,880 --> 00:20:33,240
we must act first.

280
00:20:33,270 --> 00:20:34,880
Yes, we must act first.

281
00:20:35,200 --> 00:20:36,240
I'll keep it brief.

282
00:20:36,240 --> 00:20:38,640
The first step is to find some people.

283
00:20:39,270 --> 00:20:40,110
Find some people?

284
00:20:40,110 --> 00:20:40,910
Let me ask you.

285
00:20:41,160 --> 00:20:42,440
Do you know anyone

286
00:20:42,440 --> 00:20:44,240
in Tangjing governor's office?

287
00:20:44,890 --> 00:20:45,920
Not just the governor's office.

288
00:20:45,920 --> 00:20:48,070
Also the Supervisory Bureau,
the Penal Bureau, and the Censorate—

289
00:20:48,070 --> 00:20:49,640
do you know anyone in any of these?

290
00:20:49,640 --> 00:20:50,270
Qiao,

291
00:20:50,510 --> 00:20:51,790
if I did,

292
00:20:51,880 --> 00:20:53,480
I wouldn't have gone to such great lengths

293
00:20:53,480 --> 00:20:55,160
to have you train an army in my stead.

294
00:20:55,160 --> 00:20:57,350
They don't need
to be high-ranking officials.

295
00:20:57,350 --> 00:20:58,680
Even bailiffs would do.

296
00:20:59,160 --> 00:21:00,110
Bailiffs?

297
00:21:00,750 --> 00:21:01,310
Right.

298
00:21:01,750 --> 00:21:02,110
You just need to

299
00:21:02,110 --> 00:21:03,920
have them copy the files

300
00:21:03,920 --> 00:21:06,580
and prisoner lists in their departments
for me.

301
00:21:35,830 --> 00:21:36,480
Minglu,

302
00:21:37,160 --> 00:21:38,200
I need your help.

303
00:21:38,680 --> 00:21:39,350
My help?

304
00:21:40,070 --> 00:21:41,130
Have you forgotten

305
00:21:41,790 --> 00:21:44,310
that you are the one who killed my father?

306
00:21:45,550 --> 00:21:47,810
What about Yan Xun, who rebelled with me?

307
00:21:50,200 --> 00:21:52,070
He is the Heir Apparent of Great Yan.

308
00:21:52,070 --> 00:21:53,400
What does that make him?

309
00:21:54,350 --> 00:21:55,610
If the Muhe clan hadn't

310
00:21:56,000 --> 00:21:57,880
tried to cover up their negligence

311
00:21:57,880 --> 00:22:00,340
by blaming
the soldiers defending the city,

312
00:22:01,040 --> 00:22:03,640
how could your father
and the soldiers of Zhenhuangcheng

313
00:22:03,640 --> 00:22:05,270
be sent to the guillotine?

314
00:22:06,510 --> 00:22:08,640
And that brutal Emperor of Great Yong—

315
00:22:08,920 --> 00:22:11,440
why don't you ask
why Zhenhuangcheng fell?

316
00:22:12,030 --> 00:22:14,400
Why don't you ask the high officials
responsible for the imperial city's safety

317
00:22:14,400 --> 00:22:16,160
why they killed a few imperial guards?

318
00:22:16,160 --> 00:22:19,720
That's because Muhe clan are trusted aides
of the Emperor of Great Yong.

319
00:22:19,720 --> 00:22:21,240
The lives of a few mere imperial guards

320
00:22:21,240 --> 00:22:24,440
mean nothing to them.

321
00:22:24,550 --> 00:22:27,350
They could just be killed
just to vent their anger.

322
00:22:34,750 --> 00:22:36,150
Then I'll kill you first,

323
00:22:36,590 --> 00:22:38,190
and then kill them one by one.

324
00:22:38,510 --> 00:22:39,920
You can't even kill me.

325
00:22:40,270 --> 00:22:41,420
How can you kill them?

326
00:22:41,420 --> 00:22:44,020
You're just saying all these
to make me give up.

327
00:22:44,350 --> 00:22:45,680
You're trying to tell me

328
00:22:45,860 --> 00:22:47,290
that in this world,

329
00:22:47,630 --> 00:22:48,840
I can't kill them,

330
00:22:49,880 --> 00:22:50,610
and my father

331
00:22:51,350 --> 00:22:52,790
died in vain, right?

332
00:22:54,350 --> 00:22:55,030
No.

333
00:22:56,240 --> 00:22:57,640
It's quite the contrary.

334
00:22:58,150 --> 00:22:59,480
I'm giving you a choice.

335
00:23:00,240 --> 00:23:01,030
Right now,

336
00:23:01,400 --> 00:23:03,530
you can either kill me with this sword,

337
00:23:03,690 --> 00:23:06,490
or you can use it to help me,

338
00:23:07,240 --> 00:23:09,310
so we can create a new world together.

339
00:23:10,110 --> 00:23:11,380
A new world?

340
00:23:12,480 --> 00:23:13,400
In this world,

341
00:23:14,750 --> 00:23:17,180
the lives of noble clans
are not the only ones that matter.

342
00:23:17,180 --> 00:23:19,970
Soldiers, commoners, and slaves—

343
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:21,720
our lives and deaths

344
00:23:21,880 --> 00:23:23,590
should not be decided by others,

345
00:23:23,590 --> 00:23:25,650
but should be firmly in our own hands.

346
00:23:25,960 --> 00:23:27,030
I need your help.

347
00:23:27,270 --> 00:23:28,750
Help me change this world

348
00:23:28,750 --> 00:23:31,010
dominated by the royals and noble clans.

349
00:23:34,760 --> 00:23:37,960
Then no one will die like your father

350
00:23:38,270 --> 00:23:40,530
and the soldiers of Zhenhuang cheng did.

351
00:23:46,300 --> 00:23:48,250
If you don't believe me,

352
00:23:49,440 --> 00:23:50,920
you can kill me anytime.

353
00:24:06,690 --> 00:24:08,200
The world you talked about—

354
00:24:08,200 --> 00:24:09,070
is it real?

355
00:24:19,510 --> 00:24:20,110
Qiao.

356
00:24:20,480 --> 00:24:22,080
How is your selection going?

357
00:24:22,660 --> 00:24:23,580
I've chosen one.

358
00:24:23,580 --> 00:24:24,710
Come and take a look.

359
00:24:27,790 --> 00:24:29,400
This person's name is Wang Shi'er.

360
00:24:29,400 --> 00:24:30,830
He's from Pingyang County.

361
00:24:30,830 --> 00:24:33,160
He robbed 5 tombs of princes
from previous dynasties,

362
00:24:33,160 --> 00:24:35,830
and was locked up in the county prison
by the governor of Tangjing.

363
00:24:35,830 --> 00:24:37,270
He will be exiled to Guanbei soon.

364
00:24:37,270 --> 00:24:38,640
Dig from here.

365
00:24:39,030 --> 00:24:41,090
After digging through these 3 walls,

366
00:24:41,550 --> 00:24:43,880
you will reach
the back wall of the prison.

367
00:24:44,180 --> 00:24:45,780
Leave from here at midnight,

368
00:24:46,420 --> 00:24:47,830
and you can definitely escape.

369
00:24:47,830 --> 00:24:48,440
Let me see.

370
00:24:48,440 --> 00:24:48,880
Let me see too.

371
00:24:48,880 --> 00:24:49,350
You...

372
00:24:50,110 --> 00:24:51,160
Give it to me!

373
00:24:53,160 --> 00:24:53,890
Give it to me!

374
00:24:54,160 --> 00:24:54,880
Let me take a look too!

375
00:24:54,880 --> 00:24:57,030
This person
is proficient in civil engineering.

376
00:24:57,030 --> 00:24:59,070
He knows how to observe
the terrain and weather,

377
00:24:58,910 --> 00:25:01,260
[Grave Robber, Wang Shi'er]

378
00:24:59,590 --> 00:25:00,550
and is also well-versed
in the Eight Diagrams Array.

379
00:25:00,550 --> 00:25:01,160
Let me see!

380
00:25:01,510 --> 00:25:02,240
It's mine!

381
00:25:03,200 --> 00:25:03,720
Shoo!

382
00:25:03,720 --> 00:25:04,440
-Let me see!
-Don't snatch!

383
00:25:04,440 --> 00:25:05,000
Let me take a look!

384
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:05,750
Let me see!

385
00:25:07,640 --> 00:25:08,350
Let me...

386
00:25:11,750 --> 00:25:13,640
Xiao Ran, a quack doctor.

387
00:25:14,030 --> 00:25:16,110
He's proficient at developing
various poisonous weeds.

388
00:25:16,110 --> 00:25:18,510
He was sued
for murder by a patient's family

389
00:25:18,580 --> 00:25:19,880
and was sentenced to death
with a reprieve.

390
00:25:19,880 --> 00:25:22,070
Doctor, save me.

391
00:25:35,790 --> 00:25:37,190
Doctor, is my disease...

392
00:25:37,770 --> 00:25:39,180
incurable?

393
00:25:40,510 --> 00:25:42,200
It's kidney deficiency.

394
00:25:42,200 --> 00:25:43,070
Kidney deficiency?

395
00:25:43,070 --> 00:25:45,240
What is kidney deficiency?

396
00:25:52,210 --> 00:25:56,050
[Jianghu Doctor,
Xiao Ran]

397
00:25:56,480 --> 00:25:57,540
He killed someone?

398
00:25:58,030 --> 00:25:58,960
Simply put,

399
00:25:59,110 --> 00:26:01,110
the patient he treated couldn't be cured.

400
00:26:01,110 --> 00:26:02,960
So he just fed him poison,

401
00:26:03,200 --> 00:26:04,370
saying that since he was
going to die anyway,

402
00:26:04,370 --> 00:26:06,570
he might as well test the poison for him.

403
00:26:07,400 --> 00:26:08,070
Qiao.

404
00:26:08,920 --> 00:26:10,170
Are these people you picked

405
00:26:10,170 --> 00:26:11,310
here to work for us

406
00:26:11,310 --> 00:26:12,480
or to take our lives?

407
00:26:13,750 --> 00:26:16,950
The Xiuli Army was also
a rebel army of Great Yan back then.

408
00:26:17,350 --> 00:26:20,440
Because they couldn't establish themselves
in Great Yong and Great Yan—

409
00:26:20,440 --> 00:26:21,810
leaving them with nowhere to go—

410
00:26:21,810 --> 00:26:23,410
they followed Yan Xun and me.

411
00:26:24,000 --> 00:26:24,920
These people

412
00:26:25,200 --> 00:26:26,070
are imprisoned

413
00:26:26,440 --> 00:26:27,480
and have skills.

414
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:29,750
They were imprisoned
due to misfortune and accidents.

415
00:26:29,750 --> 00:26:31,920
They are far from being extremely wicked.

416
00:26:31,920 --> 00:26:33,850
They are just right to be used by us.

417
00:26:34,550 --> 00:26:35,150
All right.

418
00:26:35,590 --> 00:26:36,270
Qiao,

419
00:26:36,880 --> 00:26:38,010
you call the shoots.

420
00:26:48,200 --> 00:26:49,660
The one up ahead! Make way!

421
00:27:47,110 --> 00:27:47,750
Everyone.

422
00:27:48,110 --> 00:27:49,040
This restaurant

423
00:27:49,270 --> 00:27:51,720
originally belonged
to a friend of mine in the capital.

424
00:27:51,720 --> 00:27:53,070
Due to changes in his family,

425
00:27:53,070 --> 00:27:54,750
she was forced to leave Tangjing.

426
00:27:54,750 --> 00:27:55,480
Therefore,

427
00:27:55,680 --> 00:27:57,440
she left this restaurant to me.

428
00:27:57,960 --> 00:27:59,960
From now on, this restaurant

429
00:28:00,110 --> 00:28:03,500
will be our hiding and resting place.

430
00:28:04,270 --> 00:28:05,070
Friend?

431
00:28:05,680 --> 00:28:06,610
Female scammer.

432
00:28:07,440 --> 00:28:09,230
-Female scammer?
-Female scammer?

433
00:28:09,230 --> 00:28:12,360
Look at this dilapidated
and shabby restaurant

434
00:28:13,160 --> 00:28:14,440
full of holes.

435
00:28:14,470 --> 00:28:16,700
Do you know
how much she scammed from His Highness?

436
00:28:16,700 --> 00:28:17,220
This...

437
00:28:17,280 --> 00:28:17,840
Plus this...

438
00:28:17,840 --> 00:28:18,600
And this.

439
00:28:22,920 --> 00:28:23,590
Song Cheng.

440
00:28:23,910 --> 00:28:24,520
Your Highness.

441
00:28:24,520 --> 00:28:25,240
Come up.

442
00:28:27,480 --> 00:28:28,340
Your Highness.

443
00:28:30,590 --> 00:28:31,720
You've got a death wish?

444
00:28:31,720 --> 00:28:32,420
So full of nonsense.

445
00:28:32,420 --> 00:28:33,000
Your Highness!

446
00:28:33,000 --> 00:28:34,000
Full of nonsense.

447
00:28:34,790 --> 00:28:35,480
Get off!

448
00:28:37,680 --> 00:28:38,350
Everyone,

449
00:28:38,920 --> 00:28:42,000
this is
the current Crown Prince of Biantang.

450
00:28:42,790 --> 00:28:43,790
-Him?
-Him?

451
00:28:46,440 --> 00:28:48,110
This is the token
of my Crown Prince's Mansion.

452
00:28:48,110 --> 00:28:49,920
It has my father's seal on it.

453
00:28:52,720 --> 00:28:54,480
Take a good look at it.

454
00:28:55,260 --> 00:28:56,870
This is no ordinary...

455
00:29:00,030 --> 00:29:01,230
When did you get that?

456
00:29:01,350 --> 00:29:02,640
If you found out,

457
00:29:02,640 --> 00:29:03,750
how can I be called a master thief?

458
00:29:03,750 --> 00:29:04,240
I...

459
00:29:04,960 --> 00:29:07,220
Who knows if you're the real Crown Prince

460
00:29:08,110 --> 00:29:09,110
or a fake one?

461
00:29:11,790 --> 00:29:12,960
If you really are the Crown Prince,

462
00:29:12,960 --> 00:29:15,710
why don't you take us
to the Crown Prince's Mansion?

463
00:29:15,710 --> 00:29:17,110
Your teeth are very good.

464
00:29:17,200 --> 00:29:18,220
It means it's being taken care of.

465
00:29:18,220 --> 00:29:18,790
Scram.

466
00:29:27,830 --> 00:29:28,750
You know what?

467
00:29:29,450 --> 00:29:30,480
The belt on his body

468
00:29:30,480 --> 00:29:31,760
is indeed a royal item.

469
00:29:32,510 --> 00:29:34,130
I've seen this kind of pattern

470
00:29:34,130 --> 00:29:35,270
in Prince Su's tomb.

471
00:29:38,040 --> 00:29:39,500
Let me take a look too then.

472
00:29:45,460 --> 00:29:48,060
The ink pad color left on his fingers
are purple

473
00:29:48,270 --> 00:29:49,530
and wasn't washed off.

474
00:29:51,680 --> 00:29:54,640
There's a scent of pear blossom
and crabapple on his clothes.

475
00:29:54,640 --> 00:29:55,550
He must have passed through

476
00:29:55,550 --> 00:29:58,480
Shengan District and Minhe District
in the Xicheng.

477
00:29:58,580 --> 00:30:00,000
Besides the royal mansions, Xicheng

478
00:30:00,000 --> 00:30:02,530
is full of residences
of nobles and generals.

479
00:30:02,590 --> 00:30:04,350
He really is the Crown Prince?

480
00:30:09,880 --> 00:30:11,240
Your Highness!

481
00:30:11,240 --> 00:30:13,070
Your Highness!

482
00:30:13,070 --> 00:30:14,790
You are all convicted people.

483
00:30:15,200 --> 00:30:16,660
Whether you were wronged,

484
00:30:16,920 --> 00:30:18,440
made a mistake,

485
00:30:19,160 --> 00:30:20,550
or were forced,

486
00:30:20,790 --> 00:30:23,190
leaving you
with no choice but to go astray,

487
00:30:23,790 --> 00:30:26,270
His Highness
brought you out of prison today

488
00:30:26,830 --> 00:30:28,720
to give you a new choice.

489
00:30:29,510 --> 00:30:31,510
You can choose to serve His Highness

490
00:30:31,920 --> 00:30:34,400
and live a new life under a new identity.

491
00:30:52,230 --> 00:30:54,650
♪ Facing the wind, I tread through frost ♪

492
00:30:54,700 --> 00:30:58,070
♪ Measuring rivers and hills,
hooves rise light ♪

493
00:30:58,750 --> 00:31:00,870
♪ The horizon lies far ahead ♪

494
00:31:01,070 --> 00:31:03,440
♪ Swaying gently ♪

495
00:31:05,500 --> 00:31:07,720
♪ Through pine mists, past 1,000 hills ♪

496
00:31:07,750 --> 00:31:11,130
♪ Wrapped in the vast moonlight ♪

497
00:31:12,010 --> 00:31:14,730
♪ Having drunk the surging waves ♪

498
00:31:14,750 --> 00:31:17,390
♪ I care not how far the road ♪

499
00:31:19,070 --> 00:31:21,470
♪ When I was young,
I penned down a long chapter ♪

500
00:31:21,830 --> 00:31:24,890
♪ I wrote poems
praising the prosperous world ♪

501
00:31:25,050 --> 00:31:28,210
♪ The wind was not yet full,
the moon not yet round ♪

502
00:31:28,240 --> 00:31:32,270
♪ Rushing me to charge forward ♪

503
00:31:33,240 --> 00:31:34,840
♪ Strong wine to the wild plains ♪

504
00:31:34,870 --> 00:31:36,680
♪ Beyond the pass,
sand blows like arrows ♪

505
00:31:36,700 --> 00:31:38,090
♪ I ride and whip my steed ♪

506
00:31:38,120 --> 00:31:39,940
♪ Chasing 10,000 miles of cloud and mist ♪

507
00:31:39,960 --> 00:31:41,410
♪ Mountains and rivers fade behind ♪

508
00:31:41,440 --> 00:31:43,440
♪ The wind crowns me ♪

509
00:31:43,460 --> 00:31:46,410
♪ Your eyes glow with flame ♪

510
00:31:46,440 --> 00:31:48,260
♪ Strong wind breaks the lute strings ♪

511
00:31:48,280 --> 00:31:50,120
♪ Playing for 5,000 years ♪

512
00:31:50,240 --> 00:31:51,740
♪ I ride my horse toward the south ♪

513
00:31:51,770 --> 00:31:53,530
♪ Endless spring beneath my hooves ♪

514
00:31:53,550 --> 00:31:54,950
♪ Hoofbeats fade away ♪

515
00:31:55,020 --> 00:31:56,590
♪ Rolling over peaks and ridges ♪

516
00:31:56,640 --> 00:31:59,850
♪ A single neigh echoes
between heaven and earth ♪

517
00:31:59,880 --> 00:32:01,820
♪ Treading on the clear wind ♪

518
00:32:03,080 --> 00:32:05,150
♪ The realm unfolds like a scroll ♪

519
00:32:06,270 --> 00:32:08,270
♪ Chasing the bright moon ♪

520
00:32:09,710 --> 00:32:12,870
♪ My spirit swallows
mountains and rivers ♪

521
00:32:27,000 --> 00:32:27,930
What's going on?

522
00:32:28,310 --> 00:32:29,070
Princess,

523
00:32:29,560 --> 00:32:31,510
there seems to be a lantern festival
on Tianque Street tonight.

524
00:32:31,510 --> 00:32:33,030
There are pedestrians everywhere ahead.

525
00:32:33,030 --> 00:32:36,430
I'm afraid we have to take a detour
to return to the residence.

526
00:33:02,080 --> 00:33:05,700
♪ The dust in the world ♪

527
00:33:05,960 --> 00:33:09,430
♪ Is blown away easily by the wind ♪

528
00:33:10,400 --> 00:33:13,200
♪ Who can stay calm ♪

529
00:33:13,860 --> 00:33:15,200
♪ And not be scared? ♪

530
00:33:15,320 --> 00:33:17,340
♪ A slight ripple ♪

531
00:33:17,610 --> 00:33:21,200
♪ Floating life hangs by a thread ♪

532
00:33:21,480 --> 00:33:24,850
♪ The more pulled, the softer it gets ♪

533
00:33:25,610 --> 00:33:28,590
♪ Who dares to say forever? ♪

534
00:33:29,290 --> 00:33:32,670
♪ Let it be ♪

535
00:33:33,750 --> 00:33:37,180
♪ Grudges and grace
were never meant to be ♪

536
00:33:37,650 --> 00:33:40,670
♪ Why must you take and demand so much? ♪

537
00:33:41,040 --> 00:33:42,680
♪ Go weaving ♪

538
00:33:43,000 --> 00:33:47,960
♪ Grand and glorious excuses ♪

539
00:33:48,640 --> 00:33:51,180
♪ We face ♪

540
00:33:51,210 --> 00:33:55,060
♪ The heavy thunderstorm together ♪

541
00:33:56,830 --> 00:33:57,830
I have roughly figured out

542
00:33:57,830 --> 00:33:59,400
the locations within Tangjingcheng.

543
00:33:59,400 --> 00:34:01,000
Centered around the palace,

544
00:34:01,110 --> 00:34:03,160
the Six Ministries
are located in the southeast

545
00:34:03,160 --> 00:34:04,440
and southwest corners.

546
00:34:04,440 --> 00:34:06,550
And the official of the Ministry of Works,
Zhang Qingzhao, whom we are looking for,

547
00:34:06,550 --> 00:34:07,550
is not among the 6.

548
00:34:07,920 --> 00:34:10,320
He belongs to
the secret Manufacturing Bureau.

549
00:34:10,320 --> 00:34:12,190
The Manufacturing Bureau is responsible
for palace reconstruction,

550
00:34:12,190 --> 00:34:13,320
Tangjing's city defense,

551
00:34:13,320 --> 00:34:15,760
and the waterways
connecting Biantang with other countries.

552
00:34:15,760 --> 00:34:18,080
They control all the open and secret files
of Biantang's city defense.

553
00:34:18,080 --> 00:34:19,280
It's a confidential office.

554
00:34:19,280 --> 00:34:20,880
As for Zhang Qingzhao himself,

555
00:34:20,880 --> 00:34:23,000
it's difficult for an outsider
to find out about his whereabouts.

556
00:34:23,000 --> 00:34:24,330
Then where do we start?

557
00:34:24,960 --> 00:34:26,889
We can only use the dumbest method.

558
00:34:27,120 --> 00:34:28,250
The dumbest method?

559
00:34:37,480 --> 00:34:38,360
Princess Fu!

560
00:34:39,480 --> 00:34:40,190
Princess Fu.

561
00:34:40,190 --> 00:34:42,320
His Highness and I
specially prepared this for you.

562
00:34:42,320 --> 00:34:43,230
Do you like it?

563
00:34:43,510 --> 00:34:45,440
Zi Ming prepared all these for you.

564
00:34:45,630 --> 00:34:47,830
She wanted to celebrate your birthday.

565
00:34:49,070 --> 00:34:51,630
Today is Princess Fu's birthday.

566
00:34:55,630 --> 00:34:56,440
No need.

567
00:34:56,889 --> 00:34:59,090
I'm not used to celebrating birthdays.

568
00:34:59,230 --> 00:34:59,900
Princess Fu,

569
00:34:59,900 --> 00:35:01,900
my family declined when I was young,

570
00:35:02,000 --> 00:35:03,200
and I was sold as a slave.

571
00:35:03,200 --> 00:35:04,760
It's all thanks to His Highness
for saving me,

572
00:35:04,760 --> 00:35:06,090
and you for taking me in.

573
00:35:06,400 --> 00:35:07,400
I am grateful,

574
00:35:07,400 --> 00:35:10,060
so I sincerely want to
celebrate your birthday.

575
00:35:12,340 --> 00:35:13,070
Princess Fu,

576
00:35:13,150 --> 00:35:14,550
take a look at this first.

577
00:35:18,840 --> 00:35:20,000
This pair of agate bracelets

578
00:35:20,000 --> 00:35:21,590
symbolizes two flowers
growing on one stalk.

579
00:35:21,590 --> 00:35:23,360
It means I wish you and His Highness

580
00:35:23,360 --> 00:35:25,220
a long and lasting relationship.

581
00:35:25,970 --> 00:35:26,740
No need.

582
00:35:26,920 --> 00:35:29,050
I don't usually like wearing jewelry.

583
00:35:30,280 --> 00:35:31,030
Let's eat.

584
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:36,600
Princess,

585
00:35:36,740 --> 00:35:37,930
this is Hong River fish.

586
00:35:37,930 --> 00:35:38,850
It's very rare.

587
00:35:42,080 --> 00:35:43,750
Do you not like this fish either?

588
00:35:43,750 --> 00:35:44,270
I...

589
00:35:44,690 --> 00:35:45,890
I'm choking on a bone.

590
00:36:01,030 --> 00:36:03,320
Are you surprised? Are you shocked?

591
00:36:03,340 --> 00:36:04,820
What are you trying to do?

592
00:36:04,880 --> 00:36:05,510
Fu.

593
00:36:06,480 --> 00:36:08,740
Zi Ming was being ridiculous last night.

594
00:36:08,920 --> 00:36:10,670
You've also been going out early
and coming back late these days.

595
00:36:10,670 --> 00:36:11,930
You must be very tired.

596
00:36:12,440 --> 00:36:15,440
So I specially designed
this house-carriage for you.

597
00:36:15,960 --> 00:36:18,150
House-carriage?

598
00:36:22,440 --> 00:36:23,960
Please get on, Fu,

599
00:36:24,190 --> 00:36:25,520
to the house-carriage.

600
00:36:27,590 --> 00:36:28,230
Qiao.

601
00:36:29,150 --> 00:36:29,840
Look.

602
00:36:30,480 --> 00:36:31,880
In this house-carriage,

603
00:36:32,280 --> 00:36:34,230
you can not only rest and drink tea,

604
00:36:34,850 --> 00:36:37,250
but also stay overnight
and use the toilet.

605
00:36:38,630 --> 00:36:39,850
This small icebox

606
00:36:39,950 --> 00:36:40,960
can store some guiling jelly

607
00:36:40,960 --> 00:36:43,030
and rose drink in summer.

608
00:36:43,280 --> 00:36:45,630
They're for you to stay rested
and refresh yourself

609
00:36:45,630 --> 00:36:46,510
on the road.

610
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:47,630
How is it?

611
00:36:48,760 --> 00:36:49,510
Not bad.

612
00:36:52,000 --> 00:36:53,190
Thank you,

613
00:36:53,190 --> 00:36:55,150
our dashing

614
00:36:55,150 --> 00:36:56,360
and charming Crown Prince,

615
00:36:56,360 --> 00:36:57,110
Handsome Li.

616
00:36:57,760 --> 00:37:00,230
It's just a small token of my regard.
Don't mention it.

617
00:37:00,230 --> 00:37:01,560
Oh, right, Handsome Li.

618
00:37:01,760 --> 00:37:03,420
I have something to ask of you.

619
00:37:03,760 --> 00:37:04,360
Go ahead.

620
00:37:04,470 --> 00:37:06,280
You are going to be an envoy
in one the coming days

621
00:37:06,280 --> 00:37:07,280
accompanying Zhuge Yue?

622
00:37:07,280 --> 00:37:08,070
Yes, Qiao.

623
00:37:08,230 --> 00:37:09,030
What's wrong?

624
00:37:10,880 --> 00:37:13,080
Based on my understanding of Zhuge Yue,

625
00:37:13,400 --> 00:37:15,760
his visit to Biantang this time
is not simple.

626
00:37:15,760 --> 00:37:17,360
He must have his own purpose.

627
00:37:17,590 --> 00:37:18,760
Whether it's for Ximeng

628
00:37:18,760 --> 00:37:20,000
or for himself—

629
00:37:20,510 --> 00:37:21,960
you must be careful.

630
00:37:24,480 --> 00:37:24,880
Also,

631
00:37:24,820 --> 00:37:27,160
[Tangjing, Biantang]

632
00:37:25,510 --> 00:37:26,960
tell me everywhere he goes to

633
00:37:26,960 --> 00:37:27,820
those few days.

634
00:37:28,000 --> 00:37:29,920
This is the main street of Tangjing.

635
00:37:29,920 --> 00:37:31,520
It's called Tianque Street.

636
00:37:31,590 --> 00:37:33,480
There are 64 districts in Tangjing.

637
00:37:33,480 --> 00:37:34,880
Tianque Street and the palace

638
00:37:34,880 --> 00:37:36,110
splits it into half.

639
00:37:36,400 --> 00:37:38,320
There are 32 workshops on each side.

640
00:37:38,320 --> 00:37:40,070
There are two markets
both in the east and west.

641
00:37:40,070 --> 00:37:42,200
The east market is mostly restaurants

642
00:37:42,360 --> 00:37:43,280
and theaters.

643
00:37:44,050 --> 00:37:46,390
The west market sells silk, gold, jade,

644
00:37:46,670 --> 00:37:47,800
spices, herbs,

645
00:37:47,960 --> 00:37:49,400
and even rare animals.

646
00:37:51,190 --> 00:37:52,920
There are 4 canals

647
00:37:53,110 --> 00:37:54,170
in Tangjingcheng.

648
00:37:54,590 --> 00:37:57,590
Among them, Furong Canal
leads to the southeast of the city,

649
00:37:57,590 --> 00:38:00,250
which is the Imperial Garden
built by my father.

650
00:38:00,590 --> 00:38:02,590
Jinshui River leads to the northwest,

651
00:38:02,590 --> 00:38:05,520
where 12 ancient temples
are located in the suburbs.

652
00:38:05,920 --> 00:38:07,550
Don't forget the purpose of this trip.

653
00:38:07,550 --> 00:38:09,350
We are not here for sightseeing.

654
00:38:10,150 --> 00:38:11,320
I can't do this anymore.

655
00:38:11,320 --> 00:38:12,000
Zhuge—

656
00:38:13,110 --> 00:38:13,970
King of Ximeng,

657
00:38:14,150 --> 00:38:15,920
we've been walking for a few days.

658
00:38:15,920 --> 00:38:17,480
You've visited everywhere in Biantang,

659
00:38:17,480 --> 00:38:19,400
from government offices
to brothels and theaters.

660
00:38:19,400 --> 00:38:20,590
Haven't you seen enough?

661
00:38:20,590 --> 00:38:21,360
Besides,

662
00:38:21,360 --> 00:38:23,150
what's so good about watchtowers?

663
00:38:23,150 --> 00:38:24,920
This is already the third one
we've climbed today.

664
00:38:24,920 --> 00:38:25,760
Your Highness,

665
00:38:25,760 --> 00:38:27,800
how many watchtowers like this are there

666
00:38:27,800 --> 00:38:28,960
in Tangjingcheng in total?

667
00:38:28,960 --> 00:38:29,800
There are...

668
00:38:32,360 --> 00:38:33,110
30 in total.

669
00:38:33,740 --> 00:38:34,600
Your Highness,

670
00:38:34,900 --> 00:38:35,860
it's 130.

671
00:38:36,710 --> 00:38:38,230
You call this 130?

672
00:38:38,230 --> 00:38:39,400
Isn't this 130?

673
00:38:40,370 --> 00:38:40,890
I...

674
00:38:42,960 --> 00:38:43,960
130.

675
00:38:43,960 --> 00:38:45,560
Let's go look at the next one.

676
00:39:05,840 --> 00:39:09,280
The audience has assembled.
The show begins.

677
00:39:09,400 --> 00:39:10,030
Xing'er,

678
00:39:10,560 --> 00:39:12,290
I know you have many questions,

679
00:39:12,400 --> 00:39:14,000
and I owe you some explanations.

680
00:39:14,000 --> 00:39:15,330
I don't know why,

681
00:39:15,920 --> 00:39:17,230
but my feelings for him

682
00:39:17,730 --> 00:39:19,380
make me hurt so much.

683
00:39:23,480 --> 00:39:24,550
You mean

684
00:39:24,840 --> 00:39:27,170
these stitches might be some kind of code?

685
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:28,400
I asked you to meet here

686
00:39:28,400 --> 00:39:29,800
to discuss a cooperation with you.

